# Phase 14: Merge AgentCallbacks into HookEngine

## Goal
Consolidate the duplicate AgentCallbacks and HookEngine event dispatch systems into a single HookEngine.

## Architecture Change

### Before
```
TurnExecutor ───► AgentCallbacks ──► 10 trait impls ──► EventBus ──► TuiSubscriber
CliCoordinator ───► HookEngine ──► 10 trait impls ──► EventBus ──► TuiSubscriber
```

**Two independent dispatch paths with 20+ event call sites duplicated.**

### After
```
TurnExecutor ───► HookEngine::emit_*() ──► 3 registered adapters ──► EventBus ──► TuiSubscriber
CliCoordinator ───► HookEngine::emit_*() ──► same HookEngine Arc (shared) ──► same path
```

**Single dispatch path. CliCoordinator owns HookEngine, passes Arc to Agent via AgentConfig.**

